When comparing the number of scandals and rumors to circulate around Joe Biden since he took up residence in the White House, it is almost astonishing he has only been in office for a year.
But while it is most likely a talented individual searching for their claim to fame, there is no deny that he definitely has a higher approval rating than Amtrak Joe.
But until then, a new theory is starting to gain some traction as the video below shows a Biden impersonator casually walking through a parking lot.
Although Biden has been given ample opportunities to prove himself competent, he continues to stumble and fumble through speeches.
While the people around him video and chant, the impersonator keeps a safe distance while pumping up the crowd.
